Toopaste
========

A simple (and tiny) Pastie clone written to demonstrate Sinatra and DataMapper
usage. Originally created by Nick Plante with contributions from Dave Everitt.

sudo gem instal sinatra syntaxi do_sqlite3 data_objects dm-core dm-timestamps dm-validations dm-migrations dm-sqlite-adapter rack-test 
sudo gem install emk-sinatra-url-for -s http://gems.github.com

cp config/settings.yml.example config/settings.yml

Default credentials changeme
